Fideuram Is Considering Banca Network Purchase, Il Sole Says

-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 
2011-06-19T10:47:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/fideuram-is-considering-banca-network-purchase-il-sole-says.html
Banca Fideuram SpA, a unit of  Intesa
Sanpaolo SpA (ISP) , is in talks to buy Banca Network Investimenti SpA,
daily newspaper Il Sole 24 Ore reported, without saying how it
got the information.  Banca Network, controlled by four partners including Aviva
Plc and  Banco Popolare SC (BP) , has almost 500 financial promoters
and about 3 billion euros ($4.3 billion) under management, Il
Sole reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at   kwong11@bloomberg.net  